properties.Name: AgentReport
properties.Description: The report prepared by the Agent on an Insurance Policy application in which they report their personal observations about the applicant.

Columns.Name: AgentReportId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Agent Report.

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Policy.

Columns.Name: AgentId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: ReportDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Agent Report was prepared.

Columns.Name: ReportingPeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date covered by the Agent Report.

Columns.Name: ReportingPeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date covered by the Agent Report.

Columns.Name: ProposedInsuranceReplacesExistingPolicyIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the new Insurance Policy replaces an existing Insurance Policy.

Columns.Name: PreviousInsurancePolicyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Policy.

Columns.Name: AgentReportStatement
Columns.Description: The contents of the Agent Report.

Columns.Name: ApplicantFinancialConditionStatement
Columns.Description: A statement addressing/detailing the financial condition of the applicant.

Columns.Name: ApplicantCharacterStatement
Columns.Description: A statement addressing/detailing the character of the applicant.

Columns.Name: ApplicantBackgroundStatement
Columns.Description: A statement addressing/detailing the background of the applicant.

Columns.Name: LengthOfTimeAgentHasKnownApplicant
Columns.Description: The length of time that the Agent has known the applicant.

Columns.Name: DocumentId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Document.
